settings.description:
"Are all of the following in place at your facility: 
1. A protocol or standard operating procedure for Intimate Partner Violence (IPV); 
2. A health worker trained on how to ask about IPV and how to provide the minimum response or beyond;
3. A private setting; 
4. A way to ensure confidentiality; 
5. Time to allow for appropriate disclosure; and
6. A system for referral in place. "
